OL,4,Catmosphere after almost 30 years
OL,6,FThroughout its working life, ERS-2
OL,7,Fcollected data on the Earth's
OL,8,Fdiminishing polar ice, changing land
OL,9,Fsurfaces, rising sea levels, warming
OL,10,Foceans, and atmospheric chemistry.
OL,12,FERS-2 was also called upon to monitor
OL,13,Fnatural disasters, such as severe
OL,14,Ffloods and earthquakes, in remote
OL,15,Fparts of the world.
